    "I. INTRODUCTIONIn the field of patent document analysis, the precise evaluation of semantic similarity between phrases poses a significant and fundamental challenge.",
    "This paper focuses on addressing this critical task, highlighting its relevance within the context of Cooperative Patent Classification (CPC).",
    "While early publications by Lent et al. [1], Larkey [2], and Gey et al.",
    "[3] laid the foundation for CPC, they also exposed limitations related to language barriers, precision, and adapting to the complexity of patent documents.",
